hey call saggermakers just the same, and these are taken in the oven, more often than not the top part of the oven is usually put with these - what we called green saggers, they're always empty, and they were put right on top purpose to fire them saggers 
ready for the next oven, you see. Is that O.K?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
Did your dad have any casual or part time jobs, or did he manage to earn enough from his occupation?
