 for this - the sake of a street, they'd know -
 well they'd see another placer come up perhaps with a coat on. He'd be coming up and - he'd put his hand up then of course there used to be a dash for who get first days drawing. This was where - how he used to get odd days drawing, you know, when he was
 
out of work the other day. Yes, he's different odd days. And boat emptying was - flints mostly. You see, a - at a flint kiln. Now you want to know what flint is. They're like a ducker stone. Well you've been at the side - on the side of the shores, well t
