ertime and boiled a kettle full of a water and scrubbed that hand. I scrubbed both hands with boiling water so you know what hands I'd got. Me mother come and caught me and she says, what are you doing? I says, teacher says I've got a dirty wrist. Says, I
 
haven't washed me clean today. Who says this? So I tells her Annie Johnson. So of course me mother did swear. I do. Although I'm supposed to go church and etc but there's times that I go off - yes. And - of course I scrubbed them and - I said like - she s
