Yes. Oh we wouldn't be paid for family shoes but if anybody else had - you could do 'em a job you know, you could clean their shoes or anything of that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
The house you were just describing was the house you lived in until you got married?
