he used to pay him sixpence a week, man as we used to call Mr Bateman, he came from Alsage, and he used to call every week, same as - a clubman calling you know. But - he used to get oddments as well, such as if we went very short we'd do - pay sixpence a
 
week to this man 'til we'd paid - mother had paid. She couldn't afford anything else, which was more than often than not we used to have to - do this, and I'll tell you another thing that - we got pretty well of oddments you know and that. And then there 
