We had temperance Sundays and all that but - and we used to sign these cards you know on temperance S
undays that we wouldn't drink and - things like that, that we wouldn't smoke, that I can remember it, not as I can remember anything different as regards - the preacher always preached on temperance on these Sundays, the local preacher or anything of that
 you know, used to preach on it, but otherwise - I don't remember any temperance activities or anything of that you know.
