\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Yes, yes. Not 
that - he - you know, went any - he would go the meetings when the voting and everything was on but not that - he went - he always used to be a home bird pretty well you know. But he was interested in politics and - we - I would hear when voting time was 
- different arguments, you know, when either me uncle came or something of that you know - would come in - me father'd be talking in the house but we weren't allowed to say anything. I would hear 'em }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13589634\charrsid9981595 arguing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595  about politics you know and - when they were talk
ing about - different - men that put up and - he would allow us, same as at one time they used to get a - quite a batch of people - of children together, vote, vote, vote, you know, they used to go and sing in the street. Well he would allow us to do it w
i
th them but - certain time, we had to be back in you know. He'd allow us perhaps - go down the street to watch some - some of 'em as was going past but if he thought it was a rough lot he wouldn't let us in case the - you know - kind of went further than 
-
 than we expected - he expected 'em to go. Same as some of them, they would go miles. Then of course he used to say we'd get - taken up in it and we - we'd be gone too far to get back at us proper time If he thought it was just in the local area he would 
let us go.
