Would there be adults leading the children then or would it just be children who decided for themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
Well, I think it was more children - say as the father was interested a lot in politics, more so than - my parents were - they'd 
say, come on, let's get a banner and go out, you know, and go round the streets singing and get a group of them together and they'd go out like that. That's how - they did -
