No, she didn't go. She went to - vote always - I don't - they never missed a vote and that is the reason I will vote on any - they always said you're - to us you know, well if you don'
t vote and you've got a vote it's - your own fault if you had bad times come along you know, you're sending what you think the right man to the - poll like and - when you don't go and vote you're giving the other man a - vote extra you see, there's - it's
 as good as two votes, that's how they used to rub it into us.
