Most evenings. He'd - he wouldn't go along the club. 'Til say about eight o'clock. And yet, he was - an organiser really for it. But he was very interested. There would be times that he would go to play - dominoes or - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13589634\charrsid9981595 crib}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
 - what they called crib, card game, because he's got medals for it I know you see so - he did have odd nights out occasionally but it was not every week, not every day sort of thing.
