\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 And Annie Johnson who you didn't like.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Florrie Johnson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Who you disliked very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
No I didn't, that's the trouble, I didn't dislike her. No. No, I didn't dislike h
er, but - she always used to find - same as us, she picked on me you know because - in one way I think she was doing a good thing. Now I do, but I didn't the time. Same as if I'd got a button off me pinafore she kind of showed me up in class by telling me
,
 pull me pinafore up and sew a button on, you know. This used to - the only thing I didn't like her about you know if - probably when I'd come - I'd been sewing all night before, making patchwork and etcetera you know for curtains or different things, I'd
 perhaps been sewing all night then come and find a - button loose and when I got in school for a bit the button was off, I'd lost me button in the bargain.
