Making too many blots on your - exercise books you know as regards - dirty works she'd call it and - talking in classes. Things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
Yes. When we used to bring us reports home we'd either get praise or - it's getting time you could do this, when I got a bed report for reading and writing - for - spelling 
and writing it'd be, and yet - I got other points as regards that. I could reckon along with the next and I would - in fact I have done in different classes, I've done the sums with girls as couldn't, I've shown them you know how to do - they'd perhaps pu
t me two girls to keep me eye on, I've done me sums all right, well will you go and show such a body how to do her sum. And she - and tell her the way she does it as she can understand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 So you were good at maths?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 You told me your mum we
nt up to school when she thought you'd been badly treated?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Were parents involved in schools in other ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
No. No, only just going - you know, for anything of that, there was no parents society or anything of that, nothing of that when I was going to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 But your mum knew this teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Was this because she was a local girl who your mum knew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
No, she wasn't a local girl, that was it. But me mother did know her before they came to have a bit extra money, th
is is probably where that other question came in. She knew when they were as bad off as we were, and me mother thought she ought to have known different. You see. She's - she lived at Alsage, you see, and she used to come up by - she used to come by train
 
and come up the station, you see, she very often called in the shop where mother traded and - me mother'd come in contact with her time or two and - you know, she kind of thought she was it and - our lot were down below, you know, wipe your feet on her, b
ut - this is - not that me mother didn't respect her or anything but - she wanted to find out but she wasn't going to have me ill used with a teacher like that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
Did the other children at the school come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
Oh yes. Perhaps they'd got a little extra, the father - father was a - got a better job or - there wasn't as many in the family and all that, but they were all working class people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatmen
t from the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
No, I don't think so. If if it was something bad - used to have to go for the cane to the headmaster which was - something terrible really if we had to go to the headmaster for the cane. Because you had to stand there, at the headm
aster's door, you know, 'til he came out, you didn't have to knock and - wait - to be asked in. What are you standing here for? And - the other teachers running out and they knew - it was embarrassing to the children, you know, to stand in the porch knowi
ng they were waiting for the cane kind of style. And - if you told the headmaster, same as as I say, if you told the truth and etcetera he'd listen out to you, you know, if you thought the teacher was being too severe. And then he'd perhaps give you }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13589634\charrsid9981595 some}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595  st
roke and another time he'd give you two. If it was severe - something severe you know, you'd talked back to the teacher, say now I once remember a lad picked the inkwell up and threw it across the class, you know, supposed to be at the teacher. Now this h
e had three strokes of the cane for. Because he'd worked him up you know to that extent as - he - she - he throw the inkwell at - off the desk at her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Which kind of children do you think were the teacher's pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Well - I haven't - I don't think u
s ever realized - I mean, any favourite. I mean, we - not that I can remember, you know, her pointing out any. I do think, in olden days, there was any individuals at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Were there any gangs or groups in the school
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 No. No, we all played tog
ether you know, or - different classes you know. Girls of - mind you there was - girls in one yard and boys in the other. But in the girls school which was - schoolyard, which was a bit bigger schoolyard, there was to sheds where in the boys there was onl
y
 one. The infants used to come in that yard at the bottom end you see. So - I presume that was because they thought girls weren't hardly as rough you know and - they had got a separate playground but they always had to come under the shed - fall in lines 
for going in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
