\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2889289 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 
No. No different. Yes, Sunday school and - walks and - although I went walks on - with - perhaps - me and me youn
ger sister and some Sunday school friends as well as - as well as schoolfriends you know, I would go out - about with them. Me father wouldn't take - after we'd left school you know, he used to trust us to go out, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Did you take an interest in politics up to 1918?
