e
nd all the while - 'til - 'til we were married in fact. She was the only one that went with me when I got married. And I didn't have a - a wedding fuss as you may say. I went to church on the pram - tram. And - this person went with me and she went back a
t breakfast time to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid469682 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11499485\charrsid9981595 Did you make new friends at the time when you went out to work?
